Subject: Re: [VB] Preheat pipe

Are you in southern California?  I got mine for my '67 at Interstate VW
when they were still in Escondido--the straight tube that attaches to
the #4 cylinder exhaust stud.  They had 3 or 4 used ones on hand.  Try
checking out their website at http://www.interstatevw.com/parts.html and
you can see if they have any left.

